	The ELM mail agent provide an encrypt utility,
users can use [encode] and [decode] to mark the section
s/he want to encrypt, when sent out the mail, ELM ask
the user a passwd, use it to encrypt the section.
	But ELM has not describe what method it use to
encrypt the message.
	Has anyone idea about ELM's [encode] method? 
What method it use to crypt? Is it secure?

